        SAVING_A_CAPTURED_PRISONER_IN_A_BEASTMAN_STRONGHOLD                  = 10831,  -- Saving a captured prisoner in a beastman stronghold and submitting archaic mirrors to Imperial guards will also result in an increased Imperial Standing.
